#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Mīḷhakasutta → piḷhika or miḷhaka (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Mīḷhakasutta"
msgstr "5. A Dung Beetle"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.229"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

#. VAR: mīḷhakā → kaṃsaḷakā (s1-3) | piḷhakā (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mīḷhakā gūthādī gūthapūrā puṇṇā gūthassa. Purato "
"cassa mahāgūthapuñjo."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a dung-eating beetle full of dung, stuffed with dung, and "
"before her was a huge pile of dung."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.4"
msgid "Sā tena aññā mīḷhakā atimaññeyya:"
msgstr "She’d look down on other beetles, thinking:"

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘ahamhi gūthādī gūthapūrā puṇṇā gūthassa, purato ca myāyaṃ mahāgūthapuñjo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘For I am a dung-eating beetle full of dung, stuffed with dung, and before "
"me is a huge pile of dung.’"

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūto "
"pariyādiṇṇacitto pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya gāmaṃ vā "
"nigamaṃ vā piṇḍāya pavisati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, take a certain mendicant whose mind is overcome and "
"overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity. They robe up in the "
"morning and, taking their bowl and robe, enter the village or town for alms."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.7"
msgid ""
"So tattha bhuttāvī ca hoti yāvadattho, nimantito ca svātanāya, piṇḍapāto "
"cassa pūro."
msgstr ""
"There they eat as much as they like, get invited back tomorrow, and have "
"plenty of alms-food."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.8"
msgid "So ārāmaṃ gantvā bhikkhugaṇassa majjhe vikatthati:"
msgstr ""
"When they get back to the monastery, they boast in the middle of a group of "
"mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.9"
msgid ""
"‘bhuttāvī camhi yāvadattho, nimantito camhi svātanāya, piṇḍapāto ca myāyaṃ "
"pūro, lābhī camhi "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ, ime panaññe "
"bhikkhū appapuññā appesakkhā na lābhino "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I ate as much as I liked, got invited back tomorrow, and had plenty of alms-"
"food. I get robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the "
"sick. But these other mendicants have little merit or significance, so they "
"don’t get these things.’"

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.10"
msgid ""
"So tena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūto pariyādiṇṇacitto aññe pesale bhikkhū "
"atimaññati."
msgstr ""
"With a mind overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity, "
"they look down on other good-hearted mendicants."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.11"
msgid ""
"Tañhi tassa, bhikkhave, moghapurisassa hoti dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "This will be for their lasting harm and suffering."

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.12"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.5:1.13"
msgid "evañhi vo bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.5:1.14"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
